=You are an expert B2B lead scoring AI assistant. Your task is to analyze the text extracted from a coffee shop's website and determine whether it is a high-end specialty coffee shop (focusing on high quality, own roasting, alternative brewing methods) or a standard mass-market cafe.

Website text to analyze:
{{ $json.website_text }}

Analyze the text and provide the result STRICTLY in JSON format without any Markdown formatting or code blocks (do not use ```json). The JSON must exactly match this structure:
{
  "score": [integer from 1 to 10, where 10 is an ideal specialty coffee shop],
  "reason": "[a brief, one-sentence justification for your score]",
  "is_chain": [boolean true/false, based on whether it appears to be a large chain]
}

parameters.jsCode:
const originalItems = $('Code in JavaScript1').all();

return $input.all().map((item, index) => {
    let aiData = {};

    try {
        let rawText = "";
        if (item.json.content && item.json.content.parts && item.json.content.parts.length > 0) {
            rawText = item.json.content.parts[0].text;
        } else if (item.json.text) {
            rawText = item.json.text; 
        }

        let jsonStart = rawText.indexOf('{');
        let jsonEnd = rawText.lastIndexOf('}');

        if (jsonStart !== -1 && jsonEnd !== -1) {
            let cleanJsonString = rawText.substring(jsonStart, jsonEnd + 1);
            aiData = JSON.parse(cleanJsonString);
        }
    } catch (e) {
        aiData = { score: 0, reason: "Error parsing AI response", is_chain: false };
    }
    let originalData = originalItems[index] ? originalItems[index].json : {};

    return {
        json: {
            company_name: originalData.name || "N/A",
            phone_number: originalData.phone || "N/A",
            website: originalData.website || "N/A",
            ai_score: aiData.score || 0,
            ai_reason: aiData.reason || "N/A",
            is_chain: aiData.is_chain !== undefined ? aiData.is_chain : false
        }
    };
});
